column16:
I have completed the 3D+ course for certification and am looking at the 3D Essentials course for use with our youth programs/coaches.  This is good stuff!  

I know there are a couple of ways of looking at this, but I would encourage you to offer the Essentials class free of charge or at lower price that currently offered - I don't want that to be a roadblock for them to doing it.
This course is well organized to see the overview of 3D coaching. 75 minutes of the course length is very accessible for those who are interested in 3D coaching.
The course was very interesting and opened my eyes to other factors coaches and parents should focus on besides just the physical aspects of sports.

column16: Great content!  This course inspires me to use every opportunity in coaching to have maximum impact with the kids I interact with. Also, bringing joy into sports really resonated with me, and it will change the way I design and implement coaching strategies.
